Brambleberry bushes could be found growing in the following locales:
* [[Maskyr's Eye]] in [[the Vast]], where the farmers cultivated them.
* [[Eshpurta]] in [[Amn]], around the fields south of the city, including near one of [[Maldiglas Turntower]]'s secret [[refuge]]s.<ref>{{cite book/Secrets of the Magister|73-74}}
